The retest conditions examine price action relative to the box boundaries. For support, the conditions check if price touches the bottom of the box while respecting the top level. For resistance, similar logic applies in reverse, checking if price reaches the top while staying above the bottom. The function uses `ta.barssince()` to ensure the retest occurs at least `input_retSince` bars after the breakout, filtering out premature signals.

